# === VIVENTIUM START ===
# Feature: Docker build context minimization (Azure ACR)
# Purpose: Reduce build context size and prevent accidental upload of local artifacts/secrets.
# Why: Faster builds, fewer cache misses, and less risk of leaking local runtime data into images.
# Added: 2026-02-07
node_modules
api/node_modules
client/node_modules
packages/**/node_modules
**/.cache
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.vite
**/.parcel-cache
**/coverage
**/logs
logs-direct
logs-foundry
uploads-direct
uploads-foundry
.local_artifacts
**/.local_artifacts
backups
**/backups
tmp
data
data-node-dual
meili_data_v1.12_dual
.git
.DS_Store
.env
.env.local
# === VIVENTIUM END ===
